row.entry:
To access the Eucalyptus User Console in 3.3.1, a user must have a
							policy that allows access to the services supported by the console. For
							example:
							{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Action": [
        "autoscaling:Describe*",
        "cloudwatch:Describe*",
        "cloudwatch:Get*",
        "cloudwatch:List*",
        "ec2:Describe*",
        "elasticloadbalancing:Describe*"
      ],
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Resource": "*"
    }
  ]
}
